text: Our 2nd dose appointments booked for the 4th. Can't wait to get them. #CovidVaccine

My #covidvaccine (Pfizer) story:
First shot - Big bout of vertigo/nausea about 18 hours post shot.  Slept 3 hours mid-day; felt better.  Mild vertigo for about a week, when laying down on right side.
2nd - Tender lump on arm.  Tired 24 hrs.
Worth it.
